    "Such documentation, primarily conveyed through natural language, supplemented with tables and mathematical formulations, serves as critical instruments in safeguarding regulatory compliance and ensuring transparency and oversight of the investment.",
    "These financial documents are highly regulated, which are important to every company.",
    "The regulations that apply depend on the type of fund to which the documents refer and on the countries in which the fund is distributed.",
    "Specifically, the regulations clearly outline the specific information that must be included in each type of document.",
